# Description
# This file is the PPP chat file for the following modem:
# 		Skywire LTE CAT1 bis Verizon Modem: NL-SW-LTE-TC1bisNAG
#
# Instructions
# 	1. 	You will need to add your APN in this file.
# 		Replace:
# 			[apn]
# 		with your APN.
# 	2.  Replace:
# 			[cid]
# 		with the desired context ID of the APN. In most cases this should be 3
#

TIMEOUT 35
ECHO ON
'' \rATZ
OK 'ATQ0 V1 E1 S0=0 &C1 &D2'
OK AT+CGDCONT=[cid],"IPV4V6","[apn]"
OK AT+CEREG?;+CESQ;+CGDCONT?;+CFUN?
OK ATD*99***[cid]#
CONNECT ''
